import React, { useState } from 'react';
import { Form, Button } from 'react-bootstrap';

const AnimalForm = ({ onSubmit, initialData = {} }) => {
  const [animal, setAnimal] = useState({
    photo: initialData.photo || '',
    name: initialData.name || '',
    birthDate: initialData.birthDate || '',
    entryDate: initialData.entryDate || '',
    type: initialData.type || 'perro',
    gender: initialData.gender || 'macho',
    status: initialData.status || 'en adopcion',
    location: initialData.location || 'casa de acogida',
    microchip: initialData.microchip || false,
    microchipDate: initialData.microchipDate || '',
    sterilized: initialData.sterilized || false,
    sterilizedDate: initialData.sterilizedDate || '',
    healthStatus: initialData.healthStatus || 'bueno',
    urgent: initialData.urgent || false,
    specialCase: initialData.specialCase || false,
    allergic: initialData.allergic || false,
  });

  const handleChange = (e) => {
    const { name, value, type, checked } = e.target;
    setAnimal({
      ...animal,
      [name]: type === 'checkbox' ? checked : value,
    });
  };

  const handleSubmit = (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();
    onSubmit(animal);
  };

  return (
    <Form onSubmit={handleSubmit}>
      <Form.Group controlId="formPhoto">
        <Form.Label>Foto del Animal</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control
          type="file"
          name="photo"
          onChange={(e) => setAnimal({ ...animal, photo: URL.createObjectURL(e.target.files[0]) })}
        />
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group controlId="formName">
        <Form.Label>Nombre del Animal</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control
          type="text"
          name="name"
          value={animal.name}
          onChange={handleChange}
        />
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group controlId="formBirthDate">
        <Form.Label>Fecha de Nacimiento</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control
          type="date"
          name="birthDate"
          value={animal.birthDate}
          onChange={handleChange}
        />
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group controlId="formEntryDate">
        <Form.Label>Fecha de Entrada</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control
          type="date"
          name="entryDate"
          value={animal.entryDate}
          onChange={handleChange}
        />
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group controlId="formType">
        <Form.Label>Tipo de Animal</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control
          as="select"
          name="type"
          value={animal.type}
          onChange={handleChange}
        >
          <option value="perro">Perro</option>
          <option value="gato">Gato</option>
        </Form.Control>
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group controlId="formGender">
        <Form.Label>Sexo del Animal</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control
          as="select"
          name="gender"
          value={animal.gender}
          onChange={handleChange}
        >
          <option value="macho">Macho</option>
          <option value="hembra">Hembra</option>
        </Form.Control>
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group controlId="formStatus">
        <Form.Label>Estado del Animal</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control
          as="select"
          name="status"
          value={animal.status}
          onChange={handleChange}
        >
          <option value="en adopcion">En adopción</option>
          <option value="reservado">Reservado</option>
          <option value="adoptado">Adoptado</option>
        </Form.Control>
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group controlId="formLocation">
        <Form.Label>Localización</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control
          as="select"
          name="location"
          value={animal.location}
          onChange={handleChange}
        >
          <option value="casa de acogida">Casa de acogida</option>
          <option value="albergue">Albergue</option>
          <option value="casa de dueño">Casa de dueño</option>
        </Form.Control>
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group controlId="formMicrochip">
        <Form.Check
          type="checkbox"
          label="Tiene microchip"
          name="microchip"
          checked={animal.microchip}
          onChange={handleChange}
        />
      </Form.Group>
      {animal.microchip && (
        <Form.Group controlId="formMicrochipDate">
          <Form.Label>Fecha de Microchip</Form.Label>
          <Form.Control
            type="date"
            name="microchipDate"
            value={animal.microchipDate}
            onChange={handleChange}
          />
        </Form.Group>
      )}
      <Form.Group controlId="formSterilized">
        <Form.Check
          type="checkbox"
          label="Esterilizado"
          name="sterilized"
          checked={animal.sterilized}
          onChange={handleChange}
        />
      </Form.Group>
      {animal.sterilized && (
        <Form.Group controlId="formSterilizedDate">
          <Form.Label>Fecha de Esterilización</Form.Label>
          <Form.Control
            type="date"
            name="sterilizedDate"
            value={animal.sterilizedDate}
            onChange={handleChange}
          />
        </Form.Group>
      )}
      <Form.Group controlId="formHealthStatus">
        <Form.Label>Estado de Salud</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control
          as="select"
          name="healthStatus"
          value={animal.healthStatus}
          onChange={handleChange}
        >
          <option value="bueno">Bueno</option>
          <option value="malo">Malo</option>
        </Form.Control>
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group controlId="formUrgent">
        <Form.Check
          type="checkbox"
          label="Urgente"
          name="urgent"
          checked={animal.urgent}
          onChange={handleChange}
        />
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group controlId="formSpecialCase">
        <Form.Check
          type="checkbox"
          label="Caso Especial"
          name="specialCase"
          checked={animal.specialCase}
          onChange={handleChange}
        />
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group controlId="formAllergic">
        <Form.Check
          type="checkbox"
          label="Alérgico"
          name="allergic"
          checked={animal.allergic}
          onChange={handleChange}
        />
      </Form.Group>
      <Button variant="primary" type="submit">
        Guardar
      </Button>
    </Form>
  );
};

export default AnimalForm;
